subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams was undone by errors and lost the Kremlin Cup final in Moscow, 5-7, 6-1, 6-1, to Elena Dementieva. Top-seeded Nikolay Davydenko gave Russia a sweep of the men’s and women’s titles by beating Paul-Henri Mathieu, 7-5, 7-6 (9).
